data.name: txtActivity.AccessibleDescription
data.value: TextBox that shows the activity occuring when the GC is run.

data.name: btnCreateObjects.AccessibleDescription
data.value: Button creating the tree of objects.

data.name: btnKillObject.AccessibleDescription
data.value: Button that sets the object selected in the lstCreatedObjects ListBox to nothing.

data.name: btnDisposeObject.AccessibleDescription
data.value: Button that calls Dispose on the object selected in the lstCreatedObjects ListBox.

data.name: btnClear.AccessibleDescription
data.value: Button that erases the Activity Log TextBox.

data.name: btnRunGC.AccessibleDescription
data.value: Button causing the Garbage Collector (GC) to run.

data.name: chkIsFinalizeSuppressed.AccessibleDescription
data.value: Checkbox that determines whether SuppressFinalize will be called when the object is Disposed.
